LanguageData.NeedMeditationSpotAlertDesc:
These colonists have a psyfocus need or are scheduled to meditate, but don't have any meditation spots available for them.
{0}

Place a meditation spot and ensure it is reachable and usable. Colonists will prefer the meditation spot near the best focus object they can use.

LanguageData.UnusableMeditationFocusAlertDesc:
These colonists are meditating near a focus object they can't use.
{0}

Each person can meditate to different objects, depending on their meditation focus types. A person's focus types depend on their backstories, traits, and titles. To see a person's meditation focus types, look at their details window by selecting them and clicking the 'i' button.
